belief that no club would object to their Under-23 players receiving a six-week masterclass from Ferguson.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 503, \"end\": 511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3469308228537543e-11, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coe added that he had approached Bob Charlton about the idea, who promised to get Ferguson to call him.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dalton\", \"score\": 0.621186957242198, \"rank\": 0.40926677604197254, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dalton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dalton\"}, {\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlton_Athletic_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9850819451072613e-20, \"text\": \"Charlton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlton_Athletic_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlton_Athletic_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3469308228537543e-11, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Scot finally called a few weeks later while Coe was in Cobham Tesco, answering before explaining his proposition.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cobham_Hall\", \"score\": 0.7060981632583211, \"rank\": 0.41623366435635933, \"text\": \"Cobham\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cobham_Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cobham_Hall\"}, {\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesco\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.402653906569804e-19, \"text\": \"Tesco\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesco\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"I did explain what my theory was because Bob had not actually told him.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dalton\", \"score\": 0.621186957242198, \"rank\": 0.40926677604197254, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dalton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dalton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He'd just asked him to give me a call.\\\"\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coe continued: \\\"So Alex rang and said: 'Oh, I thought you were looking for tickets'.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I put him through the idea and he said: 'Well, I do not know.'\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then there was a gap and then he went: 'Oh Jesus, I am already picking the team in my head'\\\".\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The two would meet in person at theBBCreview of the year in 2007, with Coe going over to Ferguson and congratulating him on giving Bobby Robson a Lifetime Achievement Award.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3469308228537543e-11, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\"}, {\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bobby_Robson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bobby Robson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bobby_Robson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bobby_Robson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was here where Coe was told \\\"yes\\\" by Sir Alex to the exciting opportunity, after much reflection.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9946876105518812, \"rank\": 0.005265276214291338, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"Alex looked at me and said: 'The answer's yes.'\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9946876105518812, \"rank\": 0.005265276214291338, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said fine.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We never said anymore other than that we'd speak again.\\\"\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the end, the British Olympic Association decided that at the time England Under-21s boss Stuart Pearce was the right man for the job, with Ferguson carrying on withManchester Uniteduntil he retired from management in 2013.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1524, \"end\": 1551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Pearce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stuart Pearce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Pearce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Pearce\"}, {\"begin\": 1650, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3469308228537543e-11, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lord Coe admitted his regret in failing to secure Ferguson as Olympics boss: \\\"We got pretty close to it.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lord Coe\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\"}, {\"begin\": 1787, \"end\": 1795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3469308228537543e-11, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Ferguson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have always laughed with Alex afterwards.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9946876105518812, \"rank\": 0.005265276214291338, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I bump into him fairly regularly.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He often wonders whether he missed out on a really good experience,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The players would have benefited a lot from him.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was one of my disappointments that I never got Alex Ferguson across the line.\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2101, \"end\": 2114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ferguson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.972951167401773e-61, \"text\": \"Alex Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ferguson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BOA decided that Stuart Peace probably had better credentials.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2136, \"end\": 2139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 2.0198384000059712e-11, \"text\": \"BOA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2153, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Stuart\", \"score\": 0.9999064405106043, \"rank\": 9.356818152924835e-05, \"text\": \"Stuart\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Stuart\", \"dbpedia\